<doc f='llvm/compiler-rt/lib/msan/msan.h' l='347'>// For platforms which support slow unwinder only, we restrict the store context
// size to 1, basically only storing the current pc. We do this because the slow
// unwinder which is based on libunwind is not async signal safe and causes
// random freezes in forking applications as well as in signal handlers.</doc>
